= content main
  p Hi {{ .name }},
  p A request was filed to reset the passord of your account with Essix.
    br
    a href={{ .action }} Please follow this link to create a new password
    |  - the link remains valid until: {{ .extra }}
  p If it wasn't you who filed the request, and you want to keep your current password, {{ "" }}
